TITLE: Episode 31 - New Year, Same State Shenanigans
DESCRIPTION: Jessie and Maddie return in 2020 to reflect back on 2019 but also discuss the craziness that has already occurred in just the first week of 2020. Government is not your ally, war is not an option and Australia is on fire. The liberty ladies vent their frustrations on how brainwashed society seems but bring it all back to the importance of the individual.
